# Render image build context = repo root, but only services/render +
# deps/cadgamefusion are needed. Exclude everything else, then re-include
# those two, then drop heavy nested build/cache dirs.
*
!services/render
!deps/cadgamefusion
**/.git
**/build/
**/build_*/
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/vcpkg_installed
**/node_modules
